version_description:
Hello! Kon'nichiwa! Bonjourno! Hola! Gutentag! Nǐ hǎo! Privet!

This update is all about improving how we welcome new people to Chip.

• We’ve slowed down our welcome auto-save. You now get your first save the day after you download Chip.
• We’ve added a “Welcome to Chip” banner on the homepage, tap on it to open a helpful and fun guide to Chip!
• If you tap on your first auto-save you can find a tutorial about how auto-saving works.

Ah, it feels like we were here just a week ago. We have a couple of slick new updates in our latest release - enjoy!

- We've Marie Kondo-d our Goals page, allowing you to now see your active and complete goals.
- We've spiced up the home page.
